{"tid":953334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"飯托「美人」遭網民大清算 涉事Café結業冇人承租","createTime":"2018-12-24T01:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T06:09:41.000Z","uid":118727,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"badb0d3cc09482aebcf7fc4efa4c303dacfe0b41","tid":953334,"uid":118727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T01:03:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181224/large/1545581109_6811.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181224%2Flarge%2F1545581109_6811.jpg&h=447193a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n過去一年「美人計」騙局肆虐全港，除了倫敦金、網上情緣外，就連「美女飯局」亦出籠，短短數月大批港男中招，在交友App被「美女」邀約到太子一間「唐三樓Caf&eacute;」食飯，結果埋單被劏到一頸血。《蘋果》放蛇直擊「飯腳妹」Karen竟一晚走11轉，成功𠱁到9男落搭，成為全城熱話，涉事Caf&eacute;經營手法亦受到猛烈抨擊，事後結業離場。<br />\n<br />\n「美女飯局」手法疑由內地「飯托」演變殺入港，據知該掠水局中，「飯腳妹」以時薪100元約港男食飯，另再拆賬單百分之四作佣金，一晚收入隨時過千元。事件不但令「飯腳妹」Karen一夜爆紅，就連美女幕後主腦亦成為全城起底對象，有受害人更呼籲所有曾中招的港男站出來向警方舉報。有曾參與「飯腳妹」運作的少女向《蘋果》表示，上班後始發現是「掠水局」，更因不忍再呃食客錢而決定中途辭職離場。<br />\n事件遭踢爆後，涉事Caf&eacute;關門大吉，記者到過位於西洋菜南街一幢唐樓的「唐三樓Caf&eacute;」，門外貼了一張通告，列明「上述單位已由業主收回，未得業主同意，任何人不得進入單位，否則送官辦理」。該通告於11月7日已貼出，但放在門外樓間的開張花牌、木架等雜物，一直無人清理，而門口牆上貼上的大批顧客舊照片仍保留。<br />\n<br />\n至於店內一面大玻璃窗則落上窗簾遮蓋，玻璃貼上地產代理招租的電話。記者致電查詢，該單位目前以每月2.6萬元放租，由事發至今約兩個月，仍未成功出租，負責的經紀坦言，如有興趣租用「價錢仲有得傾」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181224/59063589?fbclid=IwAR0ijPFEostr9HFm_nLWQzbMLxR9CzKDOZ47V5nYrjGvFwo-p1-VEO6aSPQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181224%2F59063589%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0ijPFEostr9HFm_nLWQzbMLxR9CzKDOZ47V5nYrjGvFwo-p1-VEO6aSPQ&d=JcB2XAMnINmnq8cHyxjvOtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=38210dc6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181224%2F59063589%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0ijPFEostr9HFm_nLWQzbMLxR9CzKDOZ47V5nYrjGvFwo-p1-VEO6aSPQ&h=a1110326\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181224/59063589?fbclid=IwAR0ijPFEostr9HFm_nLWQzbMLxR9CzKDOZ47V5nYrjGvFwo-p1-VEO6aSPQ</a>"},{"pid":"dffcf65b75389f8771b68ddcda03446e29246e26","tid":953334,"uid":107364,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T01:04:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06692040d6b71ae274bbc77e55e057e90c88ca38","tid":953334,"uid":54337,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T01:04:59.000Z","msg":"改個名，又開返。唔好比我睇死"},{"pid":"d5290a269a7801c4a5cb7cbdb78ddb99c7d3eb5d","tid":953334,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T01:05:10.000Z","msg":"改個名開過間"},{"pid":"6c8fe16403296f5a52b5c5a61463ba3de6f6aa40","tid":953334,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T01:06:16.000Z","msg":"一直想問起左個肥閪底未"},{"pid":"0ef4184b32a3bc96f322628b96b20396091df9c5","tid":953334,"uid":67500,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T01:07:56.000Z","msg":"起老細底好D"},{"pid":"3518f27fa326a4d9365d1e12a900989d09484a74","tid":953334,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T01:09:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 擇日復活<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e986e0f7d60f5dad662c7cf70d5f71dff491ca","tid":953334,"uid":22553,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T01:12:17.000Z","msg":"只要一日有鳩痕蠢毒撚，都會有生意"},{"pid":"98f8356ea150ac1f1e87d7fc7710cc422fa17496","tid":953334,"uid":57376,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"06692040d6b71ae274bbc77e55e057e90c88ca38","tid":953334,"uid":54337,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T01:04:59.000Z","msg":"改個名，又開返。唔好比我睇死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T01:15:00.000Z","msg":"根本無野懲罰到班人<br />\n起底又唔會無忽肉<br />\n香港法律根本縱容罪惡"},{"pid":"dc35008efab21ef081c958b4f227ce96f714271c","tid":953334,"uid":522,"li